channel.title: Need Tons of Help! I have a lot done, need final touches!
channel.description:
[b][i]I have a source, and client set up for me... the IP is all correct and it's portforwarded (the canyouseeme.com website said it saw 43594). In RS-PS.com , it said that the server was up and gave me a link to play on. I go to the link and sign in with the account stuff that I used when I tested the source with Hamachi, and it wouldn't work (error connecting to server). Please help me! I will Teamviewer or anything else that is necessary! Thanksss!!!!![/i][/b]
EDIT: Now I tried the portchecker website, and it says that the port is not available. Please help!
